Parts installation steps: 
first of all we need to put the " base " of the device
then, We put the " waist " on top of the base " So that the location of the motor to outside
after that we have to connect the " arm 01 " with The " waist "
After this connection we have to connect again, so we connect the " arm 01 " with the other " arm 02 "
Finally, we end this with connect the " arm 02 " with " Gripper " or we can say " End Effector "
< Device installation complete >
